window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Intricate anvils, magical powers, and expanded wonder.</p> <p>Noah's recent departure from Dunbar leads him into places unknown. With newly upgraded powers and items of his own creation, he must navigate a dangerous landscape, facing formidable foes while making unexpected allies. From the dark walls of Karak Hold, Noah mines to uncover unique ores. With his gains he'll develop advanced tools and machinery to improve what he creates. A lot can go wrong because with new levels and skills, comes additional danger.</p> <p>Join Noah as he crafts his way onward in this epic journey!</p>"; 
